idth: 799px) 100vw, 799px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-150\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ceramic Chronology for Monte Alb\u00e1n (from Winter 2011).<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Archaeological understanding of Monte Alb\u00e1n\u2019s history is based on the ceramic chronology devised by Alfonso Caso, Ignacio Bernal, and Jorge Acosta and presented in La Cer\u00e1mica de Monte Alb\u00e1n (1967). Caso\u2019s chronology utilized roman numerals, beginning with the site\u2019s founding in Period I and ending &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/chronology\/\" class=\"more-link\"><span>Continue reading<span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Chronology<\/span><\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-87","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/87","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=87"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/87\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5002,"href":"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/87\/revisions\/5002"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=87"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}